The paper deals with image captioning, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The method proposed uses Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) as an embedding, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the method selects the most typical caption based on unigram frequencies, which is a technique related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
